.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-2::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: chess, collecting, filmmaking, hiking, video-games, woodworking
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, water, almond-milk, tea, cola, iced-tea
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
 2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
10. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
11. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
12. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
13. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person drinking 7up##1
14. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
15. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
16. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |     3      |       4       |     5      |   6    |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | filmmaking | chess         | collecting | hiking |
| Beverage   | 7up    | cola      | almond-milk      | tea | water   | iced-tea |

