.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-3::.
There 6 different types of food: nectarine, apple, grapefruit, watermelon, plum, cranberry
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: dubstep, metal, r&b, rock, soul, trance
 1. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person eating nectarine##3
 2. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
 3. the person eating cranberry is in an odd position##4
 4. the fan of soul is on the left of the person eating apple##1
 5. the person eating cranberry is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapefruit##5
 6. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere to the right of the fan of dubstep##5
 7. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
 8. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the person eating watermelon##3
 9. the fan of r&b is between the person eating cranberry and the fan of trance##2
10. the fan of soul is on the right of the person eating plum##1
11. the fan of metal is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3    |    4     |    5    |    6     |
| Food      | cranberry | nectarine | plum   | watermelon | apple   | grapefruit |
| Music-Genre   | metal    | r&b         | trance | soul     | dubstep | rock     |

