 5. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 6. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5
 7. the person who likes blue is between the person who likes coral and the person who likes orange##2
 8. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 9. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person who likes red##5
10. the person who likes red is between the person who likes emerald and the person who likes orange##2
11. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the person who likes coral##5
12. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
13. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3
14. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
15. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3

