 4. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
 5. the person playing scrabble is the person playing scrabble##1
 6. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
 7. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 8. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the person playing backgammon##5
 9. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
10. the person playing bridge is between the person playing whist and the person driving the van##2
11. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
12. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person playing go##1
13. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
14. the person playing chess is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
15. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4
16. the person driving the bike is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |    3     |     4      |    5    |   6    |
