 9. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
10. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
11. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
12. the person drinking lemonade is the person who growsaconite##1
13. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5     |       6       |
| Beverage   | water  | tea        | sprite  | fanta     | lemonade | hot-chocolate |
| Flower       | rose | zinnia | lily | dahlia | aconite  | poppy          |

