.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-20::.
6 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, hedgehog, horse, lizard, snake
The people have 6 different hobbies: fishing, drawing, gardening, camping, cooking, traveling
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
 3. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the owner of the fish is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
 9. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
10. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
11. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5     |   6    |
| Pet         | snake    | horse | fish   | hedgehog | ferret    | lizard |
| Hobby   | fishing | traveling  | cooking | gardening      | camping | drawing    |

 